fel.cvut.cz.Board

Class Board

  • java.lang.Object
    • fel.cvut.cz.Board.Board

  • public class Board
extends Object
    The Board class creates an instance of the chess board. Chess Board is composed of 64 instances of the Tile class. Contains method for ASCII printing of the board.
    Author:
    Ryzner

      • copiedBoardSetup

        public void copiedBoardSetup()
        Sets up the copied board, recalculates the legal moves for each player, his/her pieces determines player's situation. Should be called after a move is made to update all respective values, such as number of active pieces on board etc ...
